sentences.content: The following exercises allow me to fill in the prompts given the corresponding response lists in increasingly more difficult ordering until no response list is shown.
I see her from time to [_time_].
I saw a good movie last [_night_].
I knew it right from the [_start_].
I'm tired, I have to take a [_break_].
I'm tired, I think I'll go to [_bed_].
He went skiing and borke his [_leg_].
To see better I put on my [_glasses_].
